Locale::Codes::Script_Retired(3pm) Perl Programmers Reference Guide Locale::Codes::Script_Retired(3pm)

NAME

Locale::Codes::Script_Retired - retired script codes for the Locale::Codes::Script module

SYNOPSIS

This module contains data used by the Locale::Codes::Script module. It is not intended to be used directly, and contains no calleable routines.

AUTHOR

See Locale::Codes for full author history.
